# No Open Editors Auto-Context

- NEVER rely on automatically opened tabs or "open editors" as your source of truth.
- ALWAYS explicitly read the files you need using filesystem tools (read_file).
- If you have not explicitly read a file in the current turn, DO NOT make assumptions about its contents or state.
- This ensures you are always working with the most up-to-date version of the code and prevents context leakage.
